name: WNBAHelper
0:
”Alexa, ask WNBA helper what games are scheduled for today?”
”Alexa, ask WNBA helper What games were played for last Tuesday?”
”Alexa, ask WNBA Helper what games were played on September 12, 2018”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: w. n. b. a. helper
des: This skill is not associated with the WNBA or the NBA. It provides information on the schedule for future games. For past games, the skill will provide results of the game. The skill has information on all games in the WNBA's history. This skill is open source.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
